                        "text_content": "<p>Perhatikan sintaks html dan jQuery berikut ini!</p>\n<p>Sintaks html:</p>\n<pre><div style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212); font-size: 13px; text-shadow: none; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; direction: ltr; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 1.5; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; padding: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0px; overflow: auto; background: rgb(30, 30, 30);\"><code class=\"language-html\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212); font-size: 13px; text-shadow: none; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; direction: ltr; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 1.5; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none;\"><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 156, 214);\">ul</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&gt;</span><span>\n</span><span>  </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 156, 214);\">li</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 156, 214);\"> </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(156, 220, 254);\">class</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">=</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(206, 145, 120);\">”x”</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&gt;</span><span> X\n</span><span>    </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 156, 214);\">ul</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&gt;</span><span>\n</span><span>      </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 156, 214);\">li</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 156, 214);\"> </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(156, 220, 254);\">class</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">=</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(206, 145, 120);\">”y”</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&gt;</span><span> Y </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 156, 214);\">li</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&gt;</span><span>\n</span><span>    </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 156, 214);\">ul</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&gt;</span><span>\n</span><span>  </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 156, 214);\">li</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&gt;</span><span>\n</span><span>  </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 156, 214);\">li</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 156, 214);\"> </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(156, 220, 254);\">class</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">=</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(206, 145, 120);\">”z”</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&gt;</span><span> Z </span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 156, 214);\">li</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&gt;</span><span>\n</span><span></span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(86, 156, 214);\">ul</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128);\">&gt;</span></code></div></pre>\n<p>Sintaks jQuery:</p>\n<pre><div style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212); font-size: 13px; text-shadow: none; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; direction: ltr; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 1.5; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; padding: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0px; overflow: auto; background: rgb(30, 30, 30);\"><code class=\"language-javascript\" style=\"color: rgb(156, 220, 254); font-size: 13px; text-shadow: none; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &quot;Andale Mono&quot;, &quot;Ubuntu Mono&quot;, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; direction: ltr; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; line-height: 1.5; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none;\"><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(220, 220, 170);\">$</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">(</span><span>‘li</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">x’</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">)</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">.</span><span class=\"token method property-access\" style=\"color: rgb(220, 220, 170);\">remove</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">(</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">)</span><span class=\"token\" style=\"color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">;</span></code></div></pre>\n<p>Apa yang terjadi jika script Jquery tersebut dijalankan? </p>",
